headline: Live Nation Entertainment Rises 22% in a Year: Time to Buy the Stock?
summary: LYV is well-positioned for growth in 2025 with high ticket volume and expansion of new venues, which investors can see as a compelling entry point in the year.

headline: Ticketmaster’s Oasis Ticket Pricing May Have Breached Consumer Protection Law, U.K. Watchdog Says
summary: Ticketmaster may have broken U.K. consumer law in the way it sold certain tickets for rock band Oasis’s 2025 tour, the country’s competition regulator said.
